# Student App Authentication System - Production Ready                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Overview                                                                                                                                                                             
  Implement a complete student authentication system for CipherLearn mobile/web app with:                                                                                                 
  - First-time password setup (admin enrolls students without password)                                                                                                                   
  - Standard login/logout                                                                                                                                                                 
  - Password reset via email OTP                                                                                                                                                          
  - Production-level security for 300+ concurrent users                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Architecture Summary                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **Current State:**                                                                                                                                                                      
  - `User` model has password (auth credentials)                                                                                                                                          
  - `Student` model has NO password (profile data only)                                                                                                                                   
  - Link via email match                                                                                                                                                                  
  - Admin enrolls Student record → Student must create User credentials on first access                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **New Flow:**                                                                                                                                                                           
  1. Student enters email → Check enrollment                                                                                                                                              
  2. First-time: Setup password → Creates User with role=STUDENT                                                                                                                          
  3. Returning: Login with email/password                                                                                                                                                 
  4. Forgot password: Email OTP → Reset                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Phase 1: Database Schema Updates                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **File:** `backend/prisma/schema.prisma`                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **Add Models:**                                                                                                                                                                         
  ```prisma                                                                                                                                                                               
  model PasswordResetToken {                                                                                                                                                              
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())                                                                                                                                       
  userId    Int                                                                                                                                                                           
  user      User      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)                                                                                                    
  token     String    @unique                                                                                                                                                             
  expiresAt DateTime                                                                                                                                                                      
  usedAt    DateTime?                                                                                                                                                                     
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  @@index([token])                                                                                                                                                                        
  @@index([userId])                                                                                                                                                                       
  @@map("password_reset_tokens")                                                                                                                                                          
  }                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  model TokenBlacklist {                                                                                                                                                                  
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())                                                                                                                                        
  token     String   @unique                                                                                                                                                              
  userId    Int                                                                                                                                                                           
  expiresAt DateTime                                                                                                                                                                      
  reason    String?                                                                                                                                                                       
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  @@index([token])                                                                                                                                                                        
  @@map("token_blacklist")                                                                                                                                                                
  }                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  model LoginAttempt {                                                                                                                                                                    
  id        Int      @id @default(autoincrement())                                                                                                                                        
  email     String?                                                                                                                                                                       
  ipAddress String                                                                                                                                                                        
  success   Boolean                                                                                                                                                                       
  userAgent String?                                                                                                                                                                       
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  @@index([email, createdAt])                                                                                                                                                             
  @@index([ipAddress, createdAt])                                                                                                                                                         
  @@map("login_attempts")                                                                                                                                                                 
  }                                                                                                                                                                                       
  ```                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **Update User Model:**                                                                                                                                                                  
  ```prisma                                                                                                                                                                               
  model User {                                                                                                                                                                            
  // ... existing fields ...                                                                                                                                                              
  failedLoginAttempts Int       @default(0)                                                                                                                                               
  lockedUntil         DateTime?                                                                                                                                                           
  passwordResetTokens PasswordResetToken[]                                                                                                                                                
  }                                                                                                                                                                                       
  ```                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Phase 2: Install Dependencies                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **File:** `backend/package.json`                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                 
  npm install helmet express-rate-limit                                                                                                                                                   
  npm install -D @types/express-rate-limit                                                                                                                                                
  ```                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Phase 3: Security Middleware                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 3.1 Rate Limiter                                                                                                                                                                    
  **Create:** `backend/src/middleware/rateLimiter.ts`                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  | Endpoint | Limit | Window |                                                                                                                                                           
  |----------|-------|--------|                                                                                                                                                           
  | Login/Setup | 5 attempts | 15 min/IP |                                                                                                                                                
  | Password Reset | 3 requests | 1 hour/email |                                                                                                                                          
  | General API | 100 requests | 1 min/user |                                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 3.2 Helmet Security Headers                                                                                                                                                         
  **Modify:** `backend/src/server.ts`                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ```typescript                                                                                                                                                                           
  import helmet from "helmet";                                                                                                                                                            
  app.use(helmet());                                                                                                                                                                      
  app.use(cors(corsOptions)); // Use actual config, not default                                                                                                                           
  ```                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Phase 4: Student App Auth Module                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  **Create Directory:** `backend/src/modules/app/auth/`                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### Files to Create:                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  | File | Purpose |                                                                                                                                                                      
  |------|---------|                                                                                                                                                                      
  | `types.ts` | TypeScript interfaces |                                                                                                                                                  
  | `validations.ts` | Joi schemas with password strength rules |                                                                                                                         
  | `service.ts` | Business logic (enrollment check, setup, login, reset) |                                                                                                               
  | `controller.ts` | Request handlers |                                                                                                                                                  
  | `route.ts` | Express routes |                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### API Endpoints:                                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  | Method | Endpoint | Auth | Rate Limit | Description |                                                                                                                                 
  |--------|----------|------|------------|-------------|                                                                                                                                 
  | POST | `/app/auth/check-enrollment` | No | 10/min | Check if email is enrolled |                                                                                                      
  | POST | `/app/auth/setup-password` | No | 5/15min | First-time password setup |                                                                                                        
  | POST | `/app/auth/login` | No | 5/15min | Student login |                                                                                                                             
  | POST | `/app/auth/logout` | Yes | - | Logout (blacklist token) |                                                                                                                      
  | POST | `/app/auth/refresh-token` | No | 10/min | Refresh access token |                                                                                                               
  | POST | `/app/auth/forgot-password` | No | 3/hour | Request OTP |                                                                                                                      
  | POST | `/app/auth/verify-otp` | No | 5/15min | Verify OTP |                                                                                                                           
  | POST | `/app/auth/reset-password` | No | 5/15min | Reset with token |                                                                                                                 
  | GET | `/app/auth/me` | Yes | 100/min | Get current user |                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Phase 5: Utilities                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 5.1 OTP Generator                                                                                                                                                                   
  **Create:** `backend/src/utils/otp.ts`                                                                                                                                                  
  - 6-digit secure random OTP                                                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 5.2 Email Service                                                                                                                                                                   
  **Create:** `backend/src/utils/email.ts`                                                                                                                                                
  - Password reset email template                                                                                                                                                         
  - Uses existing nodemailer config                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 5.3 Token Cleanup                                                                                                                                                                   
  **Create:** `backend/src/utils/tokenCleanup.ts`                                                                                                                                         
  - Hourly cleanup of expired tokens                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Phase 6: Integration                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 6.1 Mount Routes                                                                                                                                                                    
  **Modify:** `backend/src/routes.ts`                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ```typescript                                                                                                                                                                           
  import studentAuthRoutes from "./modules/app/auth/route";                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  // Public routes (before protected app routes)                                                                                                                                          
  router.use("/app/auth", studentAuthRoutes);                                                                                                                                             
  ```                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 6.2 Update Middleware                                                                                                                                                               
  **Modify:** `backend/src/modules/auth/middleware.ts`                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  - Add token blacklist checking to `isStudent` middleware                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ### 6.3 Environment Config                                                                                                                                                              
  **Modify:** `backend/src/config/env.config.ts`                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ```typescript                                                                                                                                                                           
  RATE_LIMIT: {                                                                                                                                                                           
  LOGIN_MAX: 5,                                                                                                                                                                           
  LOGIN_WINDOW_MS: 15 * 60 * 1000,                                                                                                                                                        
  PASSWORD_RESET_MAX: 3,                                                                                                                                                                  
  PASSWORD_RESET_WINDOW_MS: 60 * 60 * 1000,                                                                                                                                               
  },                                                                                                                                                                                      
  ACCOUNT_LOCKOUT: {                                                                                                                                                                      
  MAX_FAILED_ATTEMPTS: 5,                                                                                                                                                                 
  LOCKOUT_DURATION_MINUTES: 30,                                                                                                                                                           
  }                                                                                                                                                                                       
  ```                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Security Features                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  | Feature | Implementation |                                                                                                                                                            
  |---------|----------------|                                                                                                                                                            
  | Password Strength | Min 8 chars, uppercase, lowercase, number, special char |                                                                                                         
  | Rate Limiting | Per IP/email with express-rate-limit |                                                                                                                                
  | Account Lockout | 5 failed attempts → 30 min lockout |                                                                                                                                
  | Token Blacklist | Logout invalidates tokens |                                                                                                                                         
  | Security Headers | Helmet.js (CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options) |                                                                                                                           
  | OTP Expiry | 10 minutes |                                                                                                                                                             
  | Audit Logging | All login attempts tracked |                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                          
